sentences.sentence: Thousands of people still live on the outskirts of town in colonias, unincorporated neighbourhoods without basic services.
sentences.translation: 成千上万的人口依然生活在城市郊区——墨西哥裔美国人社区里。

sentences.sentence: The project to expand radio and television coverage in rural areas was extended from incorporated villages to unincorporated villages.
